      • dialogRequiredProperties

        public java.util.List<jfxtras.icalendarfx.properties.PropertyType> dialogRequiredProperties()

        Returned list of PropertyType values, that when changed, necessitate a user dialog to determine scope of change. If changes do not contain ANY PropertyType in the returned list then changes can proceed automatically without a user dialog.

        Returns:
        List&lt;PropertyType&gt; that when any are changed require a user dialog to request scope of change (e.g. ONE, ALL or THIS_AND_FUTURE)
